criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Bacteriological positive: including positive AFB smear/ culture / molecular test;

          -  Agree to accept this survey;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  HIV antibody positive and AIDS patients;

          -  Combined with extrapulmonary TB;

          -  Critically ill patients, and according to the judgment of the research physician, it
             is impossible to survive for more than 16 weeks;
